{"tid":1849061,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（有做請自首）最近呢個月有冇食麥當勞","createTime":"2020-01-28T22:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T04:30:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":450,"dislike":1065,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"15d8b04d2cd3cc5cb65ef8a6d9a8d900fcfb35b8","tid":1849061,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T22:42:02.000Z","msg":"由於麥當勞罷食比較遲，所以只計最近呢個月<br />\n<br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f2582dc76d4740cd03edbd51c071c632083ab7","tid":1849061,"uid":60434,"like":11,"dislike":47,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T22:42:24.000Z","msg":"麥炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0dc23d0753e4f681fae779aef6fbd0ca62dc1cc","tid":1849061,"uid":258227,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T22:44:14.000Z","msg":"冇食年半"},{"pid":"7a5a22c4953ea7d92831776d7464f7aa72744e9e","tid":1849061,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T22:47:32.000Z","msg":"原來仲有三個人有食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23da0b97be76add1f5f6145a6790645a5b3c57ec","tid":1849061,"uid":301079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0dc23d0753e4f681fae779aef6fbd0ca62dc1cc","tid":1849061,"uid":258227,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T22:44:14.000Z","msg":"冇食年半"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T22:57:28.000Z","msg":"好似最近有D M記已經由24轉做冇24啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99858a3b181e53b2bd1d7e1b8e857cf911621e20","tid":1849061,"uid":223675,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T23:08:58.000Z","msg":"香港仲有呢間野咩，點解我睇唔到嘅"},{"pid":"d7a598e01610baeaf27080e5e355e5f8ebb3d6c6","tid":1849061,"uid":133525,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"